summary: An ordinance relating to zoning and providing for the rezoning of Lots 1 and 2, Block 1, Harry D. Denny's Green Lake Addition and an unplatted tract of land 120 feet by 120 feet in the Northeast Quarter of the Northwest Quarter of the Northeast Quarter of Section 6, Township 25 North, Range 4 East, W. M., with respect to Use and Area Districts, and amending Ordinance No. 45382, as amended, by adding thereto two new sections numbered 2-83 and 17-53, respectively.
